::Feline::

She smiled at Breakdown.  "I'm sorry I don't know your name," she 
spoke in a soft purring voice, smiled and turned on the charm. "But 
you'll just ahve to wait your turn. Commander's first you know.  But 
your a sweet bot, Come by later, will ya?"

She turned to Skulletron. "I know your going to be the power behind 
what ever Zardus has planned for us, You'll have to the muscle for 
the job." She walked slowly up to Skulletron again.  She took the end 
of her tail and gently wrapped it around his neck and under his 
chin, "I'm just a pussy cat. All brains, good looks and purr to warm 
your spark. So I'll be counting on you to look out for me. Will you 
do that?" She looked him in the eyes and gently stroked her nad over 
his shoulder and down the side of his arm. She smiled and walked back 
to Zardus.  She turned to him and said in a soft and sweet voice, "So 
what's the plan great and powerful leader?" 

She placed her hand back on his shoulder and looked into his eyes.
